item.description:
Cavey's (French restaurant - downstairs) on 01/29/09 at 7:00pm.

Not many french restaurants around, but Cavey's in Manchester has been around for quite some time. I seldom eat in the downstairs French Restaurant due to the expense, but for January they are doing a pre-fix menu for $34.00. You can also order off the menu. So, let's go!!

Parking is behind the restaurant. website is: http://www.caveysrest...

Donation of $1.00 requested/not required to defray costs of Meetup.

- Betsy
